{"tid":582905,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈建議九巴車長貼錢番工","createTime":"2018-03-06T14:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T13:43:36.000Z","uid":37522,"like":91,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfeb3ee6737413230f99df6998b391a0baa5f7f","tid":582905,"uid":37522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"反正司機都唔敢企出黎，本人向九巴作出以下提案以最大化九巴之盈利：<br />\n<br />\n車長揸每程車應該俾番車費，佢地唔止享用左九巴服務，而且大部份車長係巴膠，佢哋跟本就享受緊揸巴士既樂趣。所以應該俾番錢九巴。<br />\n<br />\n另外，九巴車長可以改為自僱。向九巴租用巴士，繳交車租，油費及租巴士泊車車位。八達通收入每次上繳1%俾八達通公司另外繳交10%給九巴作行政及安裝費。硬幣收入每日收$100開箱費。如工傷病假可自行聘請代班車長，並需繳付最低工資。"},{"pid":"6a5c9883eeefbcb1f02f5f3cc77d32a145738e64","tid":582905,"uid":37522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9719b16fc016289999cefe5480eae19f3fe9cf1","tid":582905,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"繼續努力"},{"pid":"6b4eb6e38d93467e9baf0fa0ea4b9c3a55b2b45d","tid":582905,"uid":37522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9719b16fc016289999cefe5480eae19f3fe9cf1","tid":582905,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"繼續努力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T14:57:16.000Z","msg":"努力揸巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c042d57574497d866ca7acd634f1fbf7a3fc86","tid":582905,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"改自僱 咁每個月仲洗唔洗扣帛金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e5dd5a6d49064f90f56b2663a302e6b7a4d295","tid":582905,"uid":57410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"86c042d57574497d866ca7acd634f1fbf7a3fc86","tid":582905,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,